organic.title: The Young Breast Cancer Project
organic.snippet: The Young Breast Cancer Project advocates for early detection of disease through breast health education. We elevate young survivors' stories.

organic.title: The Portraits Project: A Portrait of Cancer Across America
organic.snippet: By sharing the stories of people across the United States, the Portraits Project serves as a platform to unite those who have been affected by cancer.

organic.title: Programs - The Young Breast Cancer Project
organic.snippet: The Young Breast Cancer Project (YBCP) grew from a photo project called the Breast Cancer Portrait Project (BCPP), spearheaded by our founder, Missy Peters.
